{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotation"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The annotation object to remove. This object must conform","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol","type":"text"}]}],"name":"annotation"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Removing an annotation object dissociates it from the map view entirely,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"preventing it from being displayed on the map. Thus you would typically call","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this method only when you want to hide or delete a given annotation.","type":"text"}]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"metadata":{"title":"removeAnnotation:","symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1820","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"roleHeading":"Instance Method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)removeAnnotation:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotation:"},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Removes an annotation from the map view, deselecting it if it is selected.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotation:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/removeAnnotation:":{"type":"topic","title":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotation:","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotation:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Removes an annotation from the map view, deselecting it if it is selected."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotation:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","title":"MLNMapView","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"role":"collection"}}}